{
  "chapter": 44,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十四回 八方风雨\n\n七妙神君梅山民在大戢岛上为辛捷和吴凌风讲解天竺身法的精妙之处，随后三人商议向崆峒、武当、峨嵋三大宗派投下拜柬，邀约他们在月圆之夜于五华山一会，了结十五年前的恩怨。辛捷和吴凌风辗转投发拜柬后，与梅山民一同赶赴五华山。\n\n月圆之夜，五华山老梅树下，梅山民、辛捷、吴凌风三人静候强敌。崆峒掌门厉鹗、武当赤阳道长、峨嵋苦庵上人、点苍落英剑客谢长卿四大宗派掌门人如约而至。厉鹗手持被他夺走的梅香剑，辛捷怒斥其偷窃之行。双方言语交锋后，四大掌门布下剑阵围攻辛捷和吴凌风。\n\n激战中，厉鹗等人使出拼命招式\"九死一生\"，辛捷和吴凌风以大衍神剑和断魂剑绝招反击，最终逼退四大掌门。吴凌风豪气干云，邀敌再战。然而厉鹗目光中闪过狠毒神色，梅香剑在手，战斗仍在继续。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "吴贤侄，你最近也是迭有遇合，尤其那梵文所载的轻功，必定是高明无比的了，你且施展出来见识见识？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当今天下，轻功身法当推慧大师的'诘摩神步'最为神妙，但论起速度，恐仍不及这种天竺身法！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "早年老朽闯荡江湖时，也曾风闻天竺有一种旁门的武学，但都始终没有流传到中土，看来果是所传不虚了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "text": "我和大哥这一次赶来，是想请梅叔叔作主……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "speaker_name": "梅山民",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "很好！你们也真不忘老一辈的教诲，这一段十余年的公案，我想也应该有一个了断了……",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "text": "一路来已在崆峒、武当两处投下拜柬，邀约他们在月圆之日在五华山上一会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_mei_shan_min",
      "text": "此去峨嵋不远，今日就去走一遭，去给苦庵上人也投一张拜帖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "月儿即将当空了，怎么……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "捷弟莫要心焦，那些人物背着如此的大名头，一定不会老着脸皮避而不战的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "贼子们还不快来，对了，大哥，待会咱们要好好折辱他们一番……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_e",
      "speaker_name": "厉鹗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "辛捷那小子看样子还没有到呢！……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_e",
      "speaker_name": "厉鹗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "月儿已登中天，看来辛捷是不会来的了？咱们且等他一会……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_li_e",
      "text": "不敢当，咱们早已恭候大驾！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_e",
      "speaker_name": "厉鹗",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "好说！好说……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_li_e",
      "text": "废话少说两句，咱们这就动手——",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_e",
      "speaker_name": "厉鹗",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "姓吴的，咱们是一江二海之恨，就是你不找上门来，我厉某人也得找到你，你且不要急——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_yang_dao_zhang",
      "speaker_name": "赤阳道长",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "吴施主不要心急，断魂剑和七妙神君后代的召唤，咱们哪敢违命！嘿，苦庵上人，你说是吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "晚辈斗胆投下请柬，请各位大英雄到这儿来，拜赐神功，致使各位千里奔波，实令晚辈内心不安。好在各位都是一代宗师，必然不会计较于此……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_e",
      "speaker_name": "厉鹗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好说好说，咱们这叫作旧地重游，面对高山古梅，心旷神怡，辛小侠乃是七妙后代，到底不是俗人——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": "char_li_e",
      "text": "姓厉的少逞口舌之利，你作恶半生，日常在江湖上以阴诈欺人，今日便是你的死期，闲话倒可以少说两句。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_e",
      "speaker_name": "厉鹗",
      "listener": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "text": "姓吴的小子如此自大，咱们走着瞧——",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_e",
      "speaker_name": "厉鹗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "过来吧，厉某人领教神君和断魂剑的真传——",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_e",
      "speaker_name": "厉鹗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "故人有后，咱们老一辈的再不尽力，岂不叫他们耻笑？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_li_e",
      "text": "亏你身为掌门，竟然偷窃别人之物——",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_e",
      "speaker_name": "厉鹗",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "你敢发招吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玄门正宗，名门大派的剑法不过如此而已！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ling_feng",
      "speaker_name": "吴凌风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "再上来吧——",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 44,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    }
  ],
